data.name: Inviting Rondo of the Mikanko
data.desc: Equip to an opponent's monster. Take control of it while you control a "Mikanko" monster, but it cannot activate its effects while you control it. When this card leaves the field, send the equipped monster to the GY. You can only control 1 "Inviting Rondo of the Mikanko". You can only activate 1 "Inviting Rondo of the Mikanko" per turn.
